I want to get home quickly, so I'm serious.

I have a name you know? Alice.

can really make your wish come true?

"So I…thought if I just follow his instructions,
someone would tell me the way…
Whenever one is lost, things get interpreted
in a way that suits the person.
"The King saw you were in a trouble,
and lied to try to take advantage of you.
Everyone in this world (including Alice) is mad.'
Now that you understand, I understand as well.
I don't know what you're talking about…

But you keep trying to ignore it.
to keep you from turning completely mad.
…I am you, and you are me.

towards anything that doesn't please her.

how to make Pseudo Sea Turtle Soup.

You just told me that you'd do whatever I wanted!
I now feel like torturing you!
"What do you plan on doing with me…?
why don't I eat you right up?!!
